                'C) Risk Assessment, Resuscitation, Supportive Care, Investigations, Decontamination, Enhanced Elimination, Antidotes, Disposition',
                'D) Resuscitation, Risk Assessment, Supportive Care, Interventions, Decontamination, Extracorporeal Elimination, Antidotes, Disposition',
